node.text:
You're not your job. You're not how much money you have in the bank. You're not the car you drive. You're not the contents of your wallet.. You're the all-singing, all-dancing energy of the world.

This has stuck with me for years, from one of my fav movies of all time with a word changed to make it a lil more family friendly to post 😅 happy Friday all 

📸 @simon_j_morton
